# Keeps the Docker build context small and prevents host-built artifacts
# (which may carry host-OS native binaries — esbuild/rollup/bcrypt — or a
# local .env) from being copied into the image by `COPY . .` (Dockerfile,
# apps/web/Dockerfile).

.git/
**/node_modules/
**/dist/
**/coverage/
# tsc -b incremental build state: a host tsbuildinfo copied into the image
# makes `tsc -b` believe a sibling package's dist (excluded above) is already
# built, failing with TS6305 "Output file has not been built from source".
**/*.tsbuildinfo

.env
.env.*
!.env.example

*.log
npm-debug.log*

.vscode/
.idea/

.claude/
docs/
README.md
CONTRIBUTING.md
